#: ../../src/Plugins/Atelier/Commanding/Meta/MetaCommand.cs:200
msgid "    :transient compiles against the current session, runs as a probe, then discards its changes."
msgstr "    :transient 会基于当前会话编译并作为一次探测运行，随后丢弃它带来的更改。"

#: ../../src/Plugins/Atelier/Commanding/Meta/MetaCommand.cs:207
#, csharp-format
msgid "    {0} - {1}"
msgstr "    {0} - {1}"

#: ../../src/Plugins/Atelier/Commanding/Meta/MetaCommand.cs:213
msgid "    An unfinished Task returned as the result is also tracked by the window indicator."
msgstr "    若结果返回的是尚未完成的 Task，窗口指示器也会继续跟踪它。"

#: ../../src/Plugins/Atelier/Commanding/Meta/MetaCommand.cs:195
msgid "    Atelier is a Roslyn C# script session, not a line-by-line shell."
msgstr "    Atelier 是一个基于 Roslyn 的 C# 脚本会话，不是按行执行的 shell。"

#: ../../src/Plugins/Atelier/Commanding/Meta/MetaCommand.cs:212
msgid "    Background execution Tasks are available as PendingTasks; LastTask is the newest one."
msgstr "    后台执行的 Task 可通过 PendingTasks 访问；其中最新的是 LastTask。"

#: ../../src/Plugins/Atelier/Commanding/Meta/MetaCommand.cs:219
msgid "    Blocking APIs that ignore tokens still need explicit cancellation-aware design."
msgstr "    对于忽略令牌的阻塞式 API，仍需要显式设计取消感知逻辑。"

#: ../../src/Plugins/Atelier/Commanding/Meta/MetaCommand.cs:215
msgid "    Cancellation injection mainly prevents runaway loops from surviving a closed session."
msgstr "    取消注入主要是为了防止失控循环在会话关闭后还继续存活。"

#: ../../src/Plugins/Atelier/Commanding/Meta/MetaCommand.cs:221
msgid "    Closing the REPL releases the surface and session automatically."
msgstr "    关闭 REPL 时会自动释放交互界面和会话。"

#: ../../src/Plugins/Atelier/Commanding/Meta/MetaCommand.cs:227
msgid "    Diagnostics, completions, and signature help describe the draft in accumulated context."
msgstr "    诊断、补全和签名帮助都会基于累积上下文来说明当前草稿。"

#: ../../src/Plugins/Atelier/Commanding/Meta/MetaCommand.cs:225
msgid "    Enter follows Roslyn's complete-submission check; unfinished blocks stay open."
msgstr "    Enter 会遵循 Roslyn 的完整提交检查；未完成的代码块会继续保持打开。"

#: ../../src/Plugins/Atelier/Commanding/Meta/MetaCommand.cs:198
msgid "    Later drafts see earlier declarations, imports, references, and loaded submissions."
msgstr "    后续草稿可以看到前面声明的内容、导入、引用以及已加载的提交。"

#: ../../src/Plugins/Atelier/Commanding/Meta/MetaCommand.cs:216
msgid "    Loops check Cancellation automatically, so intentional long-running loops can stop on close."
msgstr "    循环会自动检查 Cancellation，因此有意设计的长时间循环也能在关闭时停止。"

#: ../../src/Plugins/Atelier/Commanding/Meta/MetaCommand.cs:199
msgid "    Meta commands start with ':' and are intercepted before C# compilation."
msgstr "    元命令以 ':' 开头，会在 C# 编译前被拦截处理。"

#: ../../src/Plugins/Atelier/Commanding/Meta/MetaCommand.cs:197
msgid "    Normal submissions that change state are committed to session history."
msgstr "    会改变状态的常规提交会写入会话历史。"

#: ../../src/Plugins/Atelier/Commanding/Meta/MetaCommand.cs:228
msgid "    Pair closers can stay virtual until typed through."
msgstr "    成对闭合符在真正输入补齐前，可以保持为虚拟状态。"

#: ../../src/Plugins/Atelier/Commanding/Meta/MetaCommand.cs:223
msgid "    Reset clears committed history and restores baseline imports."
msgstr "    Reset 会清除已提交的历史，并恢复基础导入。"

#: ../../src/Plugins/Atelier/Commanding/Meta/MetaCommand.cs:222
msgid "    Session disposal cancels pending work, clears PendingTasks, and unloads script contexts."
msgstr "    释放会话时会取消挂起工作、清空 PendingTasks，并卸载脚本上下文。"

#: ../../src/Plugins/Atelier/Commanding/Meta/MetaCommand.cs:226
msgid "    Shift+Enter always inserts a line; paste mode uses Ctrl+Enter to submit once."
msgstr "    Shift+Enter 始终插入换行；粘贴模式下使用 Ctrl+Enter 一次性提交。"

#: ../../src/Plugins/Atelier/Commanding/Meta/MetaCommand.cs:229
msgid "    Shift+Tab formats the draft without submitting."
msgstr "    Shift+Tab 会格式化草稿，但不会提交。"

#: ../../src/Plugins/Atelier/Commanding/Meta/MetaCommand.cs:218
msgid "    Task.Run/Thread/Timer callbacks are guarded so detached work also observes cancellation."
msgstr "    Task.Run/Thread/Timer 的回调会受到保护，让脱离主流程的工作也能感知取消。"

#: ../../src/Plugins/Atelier/Commanding/Meta/MetaCommand.cs:196
msgid "    The editor analyzes committed history plus the current draft as one synthetic script."
msgstr "    编辑器会把已提交的历史与当前草稿合并起来，按一份合成脚本来分析。"

#: ../../src/Plugins/Atelier/Commanding/Meta/MetaCommand.cs:214
msgid "    The session Cancellation token is available as Cancellation."
msgstr "    会话的 CancellationToken 可通过 Cancellation 访问。"

#: ../../src/Plugins/Atelier/Commanding/Meta/MetaCommand.cs:217
msgid "    Token-aware calls may get Cancellation appended automatically when a safe overload exists."
msgstr "    支持令牌的调用在存在安全重载时，可能会自动追加 Cancellation 参数。"

#: ../../src/Plugins/Atelier/Commanding/Meta/MetaCommand.cs:211
msgid "    Top-level await may keep running in background after the prompt returns."
msgstr "    顶层 await 在提示符返回后，仍可能继续在后台运行。"

